{"tid":524343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【僭建風波】梁君彥否決提出緊急質詢或休會辯論 指無迫切性","createTime":"2018-01-09T13:19:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-09T13:25:28.000Z","uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"12e3796233d4ac9d57a75833aa3a0249c1936a73","tid":524343,"uid":84436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T13:19:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%83%AD%E5%BB%BA%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E6%A2%81%E5%90%9B%E5%BD%A5%E5%90%A6%E6%B1%BA%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E8%B3%AA%E8%A9%A2%E6%88%96%E4%BC%91%E6%9C%83%E8%BE%AF%E8%AB%96-%E6%8C%87%E7%84%A1%E8%BF%AB%E5%88%87%E6%80%A7-112500781.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E5%2583%25AD%25E5%25BB%25BA%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B3%25A2-%25E6%25A2%2581%25E5%2590%259B%25E5%25BD%25A5%25E5%2590%25A6%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E6%258F%2590%25E5%2587%25BA%25E7%25B7%258A%25E6%2580%25A5%25E8%25B3%25AA%25E8%25A9%25A2%25E6%2588%2596%25E4%25BC%2591%25E6%259C%2583%25E8%25BE%25AF%25E8%25AB%2596-%25E6%258C%2587%25E7%2584%25A1%25E8%25BF%25AB%25E5%2588%2587%25E6%2580%25A7-112500781.html&d=CLs%2FCSULAZ2phu0cgJ4cPZWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=166e1f58\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E5%83%AD%E5%BB%BA%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E6%A2%81%E5%90%9B%E5%BD%A5%E5%90%A6%E6%B1%BA%E6%8F%90%E5%87%BA%E7%B7%8A%E6%80%A5%E8%B3%AA%E8%A9%A2%E6%88%96%E4%BC%91%E6%9C%83%E8%BE%AF%E8%AB%96-%E6%8C%87%E7%84%A1%E8%BF%AB%E5%88%87%E6%80%A7-112500781.html</a><br />\n<br />\n【星島日報報道】新任律政司司長鄭若驊住所被揭發有僭建。立法會主席梁君彥不批准民主黨議員林卓廷，在明天立法會大會上，提出緊急質詢或休會辯論。梁君彥表示，議題並無迫切重要性，認為議員可循其他渠道跟進。<br />\n<br />\n林卓廷早前去信梁君彥，要求根據《議事規則》，動議在明日會議辯論僭建事件對政治委任制度的影響。<br />\n<br />\n梁君彥透過秘書指，議員即使不在會議進行辯論，亦不會失去表達意見的機會，決定不批准要求。"},{"pid":"162c2341632e7a982bd9806185d92da40db66103","tid":524343,"uid":7699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T13:20:57.000Z","msg":"一見到梁君彥三個字就諗起梁耀忠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4554e6a21d56648a57974a57e65b10c038171aaa","tid":524343,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"162c2341632e7a982bd9806185d92da40db66103","tid":524343,"uid":7699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T13:20:57.000Z","msg":"一見到梁君彥三個字就諗起梁耀忠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T13:24:51.000Z","msg":"宗仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1e0e2b2c9ba48f8ffb45218cce8d8c9a62dec2d","tid":524343,"uid":118125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"162c2341632e7a982bd9806185d92da40db66103","tid":524343,"uid":7699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T13:20:57.000Z","msg":"一見到梁君彥三個字就諗起梁耀忠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T13:25:28.000Z","msg":"一諗起梁耀忠就想起石禮謙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}